OL,7,FA patient says he has "lost all trust"
OL,8,Fin the NHS after finding out he'd been
OL,9,Fa victim of a disgraced doctor via a
OL,10,Fletter - five years after it happened.
OL,12,FPeter, whose identity ITV News is
OL,13,Fprotecting, was treated by Dr Luliu
OL,14,FStan in the emergency department of
OL,15,FRoyal Cornwall Hospital.
OL,17,FDr Stan has since been found to have
OL,18,Fsubjected patients to unnecessary
OL,19,Fintimate procedures, including the
OL,20,Fadministration of rectal medication,
OL,21,Ffor his own sexual gratification.
