OL,4,Cdisgraced doctor five years after in
OL,5,CNHS letter
OL,7,FHe was struck off the UK medical
OL,8,Fregister earlier this year for
OL,9,Fmisconduct, after an investigation by
OL,10,Fthe General Medical Council and a
OL,11,Ftribunal.
OL,13,FA previous investigation by the Royal
OL,14,FCornwall Hospitals found Dr Stan had
OL,15,Fprescribed and administered rectal
OL,16,Fmedication on over 200 occasions -
OL,17,Fsometimes giving it to the same
OL,18,Fpatient multiple times.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
