OL,7,FPeter was informed he had been a
OL,8,Fvictim of Dr Stan when he received a
OL,9,Fletter from the hospital five years
OL,10,Fafter his treatment.
OL,12,FHe now lives with the knowledge he may
OL,13,Fnever get answers about what really
OL,14,Fhappened to him. He says he is angry,
OL,15,Fupset and now needs medication to
OL,16,F"numb" those emotions.
