OL,3,CPatient told he'd been victim of
OL,4,Cdisgraced doctor five years after in
OL,5,CNHS letter
OL,7,F"The trust I have now with the NHS has
OL,8,Fgone," he said. "For days after, I was
OL,9,Ftrying to think back to that time I
OL,10,Fwas in hospital, trying to think about
OL,11,Fevery detail."
OL,13,FPeter was being treated in the
OL,14,Femergency department. He was
OL,15,Fadministered pain relief by Dr Stan in
OL,16,Fthe form of a suppository, and then
OL,17,Ftold to sleep.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
