OL,3,CPatient told he'd been victim of
OL,4,Cdisgraced doctor five years after in
OL,5,CNHS letter
OL,7,FHe said: "There was no offer of a
OL,8,Fchaperone. After the medicine was
OL,9,Fprescribed, and being taken into this
OL,10,Fdark room and told to go to sleep, my
OL,11,Fbiggest fear is what happened
OL,12,Fafterwards? I still don't know to this
OL,13,Fday. I did fall asleep, but I don't
OL,14,Fknow what happened after that."
OL,16,FIn January 2024, a number of patients
OL,17,Fwere told by the Royal Cornwall
OL,18,FHospitals NHS Trust that details of
OL,19,Ftheir treatment would form part of the
OL,20,Ftribunal hearing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
