OL,4,Cdisgraced doctor five years after in
OL,5,CNHS letter
OL,7,FIn July, the trust wrote to another
OL,8,Fgroup of former patients, including
OL,9,FPeter, to tell them Dr Stan had given
OL,10,Fthem rectal medication when they were
OL,11,Fin hospital, and that in other cases
OL,12,Fthe tribunal had found his actions had
OL,13,Fbeen sexually motivated.
OL,15,FPeter says receiving that news by
OL,16,Fletter was "horrible" to deal with.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
