OL,3,CPatient told he'd been victim of
OL,4,Cdisgraced doctor five years after in
OL,5,CNHS letter
OL,7,FHe said: "I have angry moments, I've
OL,8,Factually gone on to medication now to
OL,9,Ftry and numb it down a bit. It leaves
OL,10,Fyou angry, upset and it causes you a
OL,11,Flot of stress as well. I'm probably
OL,12,Fnever going know what actually
OL,13,Fhappened, and I think that's going to
OL,14,Fbe the hardest part to live with."
OL,16,FDr Stan qualified in Romania in 2007.
OL,17,FHis was a Locum Senior House Officer
OL,18,Fin Trauma and Orthopaedics for the
OL,19,FRoyal Cornwall Hospitals NHS Trust
OL,20,Fbetween 2017 and 2020.
