OL,7,FA number of legal firms have now taken
OL,8,Fup the cases of patients treated by Dr
OL,9,FStan. Enable Law in Truro is
OL,10,Frepresenting over 25 patients
OL,11,Finvolved, including Peter. It's
OL,12,Fcalling for immediate counselling
OL,13,Fsupport to be put in place, and an
OL,14,Findependent investigation into
OL,15,Fhospital practices.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
