OL,7,FSolicitor Mike Bird told ITV News:
OL,8,F"There needs to be some independent
OL,9,Fscrutiny of what happened and how it
OL,10,Fcan have happened for so long. There
OL,11,Fwere policies and guidelines in place
OL,12,Fthat were ignored by this doctor for
OL,13,Ffive years, and he seems to have
OL,14,Fmanaged to conceal it from all his
OL,15,Fwork colleagues for five years, and
OL,16,Fthat's quite difficult to believe.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
