OL,5,CNHS letter
OL,7,F"What we say is that because of that,
OL,8,Fthere needs to be independent
OL,9,Fscrutiny, and I'm afraid it's not
OL,10,Fenough we say for the trust to look
OL,11,Finto it themselves. They've got to
OL,12,Fhave somebody impartial and
OL,13,Findependent leading that
OL,14,Finvestigation."
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the Royal Cornwall
OL,17,FHospitals NHS Trust said: "We are
OL,18,Fcompletely committed to openness and
OL,19,Fcandour and take our responsibilities
OL,20,Fto the former patients of Dr Stan very
OL,21,Fseriously.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
