OL,3,CPatient told he'd been victim of
OL,4,Cdisgraced doctor five years after in
OL,5,CNHS letter
OL,7,F"We are deeply sorry for the distress
OL,8,Fcaused by his serious professional
OL,9,Fmisconduct and his abuse of the trust
OL,10,Fplaced in him by patients. We want to
OL,11,Freiterate our apology to everyone
OL,12,Fimpacted by these distressing events.
OL,13,FOur paramount priority is to support
OL,14,Fthose impacted by his actions.
OL,16,F"We have written to former patients of
OL,17,FDr Stan to provide them with the
OL,18,Fopportunity to speak with our team to
OL,19,Faccess psychological support and
OL,20,Fcounselling, tailored to their
OL,21,Findividual needs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
